               <p>Second London Jury.</p>
               <p>652. 
               
                  <persName id="t18290219-126-defend1198" type="defendantName">
                     THOMAS 
                     JONES
                  <interp inst="t18290219-126-defend1198" type="surname" value="JONES"></interp>
